remarkable degree,

00:40:07.510 --> 00:40:11.254
a high degree of correspondence
so that we really can speak of a

00:40:11.254 --> 00:40:14.167
relatively stable textual
tradition but still some

00:40:14.167 --> 00:40:15.947
fluidity.
And that's going to be

00:40:15.947 --> 00:40:17.550
